data.title: Avril Lavigne Was Born in Belleville
data.meta_description: Avril Lavigne Was Born in Belleville - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Avril Lavigne was born in Belleville, Ontario, Canada in 1984. At age 16, she moved to Manhattan to work on her debut album and dropped out of high school after securing a record deal. She released her breakthrough debut single "Complicated" in 2002 at age 18 from her 6x platinum debut album "Let Go." Lavigne has gone on to become one of the top-selling artists worldwide with over 10.25 million albums certified in the US alone.
